<div id="Layer1" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:275px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2"> <p align="left"><font class="atitulohistoria"><b> O Destino da M&uacute;sica</b></font></p><p align="left"><font class="anomeautores"><b> Ant&oacute;nio Torrado</b></font><br><font class="aprofissao"><b>escreveu</b></font></p><p align="left"><font class="anomeilustrador"> <b>Cristina Malaquias</b></font><br><font class="aprofissao"><b>ilustrou</b></font></p></td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20">&nbsp;</td><td width="50%"> <img align="right" border="0" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer2','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer1','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer2" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:275px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Era uma vez uma m&uacute;sica, uma melodia. Andou pelos ouvidos das pessoas. 
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Alguns cantarolavam-na. Outros assobiavam-na. Fosse em l&aacute;-l&aacute;-l&aacute;, no c&eacute;u da boca, ou em tri-ti-ti, na ponta dos l&aacute;bios, sabia sempre bem.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer2','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer1','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer3','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer2','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer3" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:275px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">	Quando era tocada no coreto da pra&ccedil;a, as pessoas paravam de conversar e aproximavam-se p&eacute; ante p&eacute;, meneando a cabe&ccedil;a ao som da m&uacute;sica. E, quando a m&uacute;sica acabava, batiam palmas entusiasmadas, que tanto se destinavam &agrave; m&uacute;sica como &agrave; banda que apuradamente a tocara. E pediam "Bis! Bis!".</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer3','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer2','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer4','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer3','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer4" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:275px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">	&Agrave;s vezes, o maestro fazia-lhes a vontade. Nova sess&atilde;o do encantamento e, no fim, mais uma grande <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[1],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">revoada</a> de palmas.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">	Acontecia as pessoas acordarem, de manh&atilde;, com a m&uacute;sica a rodopiar nos ouvidos. Era bom.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer4','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer3','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer5','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer4','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer5" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:275px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">	Acontecia as pessoas adormecerem, &agrave; noite, com a m&uacute;sica a rodopiar nos ouvidos. Tamb&eacute;m era bom.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer5','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer4','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer6','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer5','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer6" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:275px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">	E, durante o dia, os carpinteiros, a serrarem, assobiavam-na, as lavadeiras, a lavarem, cantavam-na, e toda a gente, quer estivesse a trabalhar quer fosse dar um passeio solit&aacute;rio pelo campo, espalhava-a pelos ares, dando mais vida &agrave; m&uacute;sica que serpenteava, feliz, em direc&ccedil;&atilde;o &agrave;s nuvens.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer6','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer5','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer7','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer6','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer7" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:275px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">	Mas a banda deu a conhecer outras melodias. Era seu dever valorizar-se e renovar o repert&oacute;rio. N&atilde;o podia estar s&oacute; a tocar as mesmas m&uacute;sicas de antigamente.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">	Porque &eacute; que n&atilde;o voltam a tocar aquela que come&ccedil;a assim: L&aacute;-l&aacute;-l&aacute;...? - perguntava algu&eacute;m, com saudades da velha m&uacute;sica.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer7','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer6','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer8','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer7','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer8" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:275px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">	N&atilde;o havia quem soubesse responder.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">A pouco e pouco, a m&uacute;sica foi-se apagando das mem&oacute;rias. 
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Para onde v&atilde;o as melodias que nunca mais s&atilde;o tocadas?
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">	Eu sei, isto &eacute;, julgo saber. Os sons sobem.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer8','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer7','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer9','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer8','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer9" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:275px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%"> Seja de flauta, de harpa ou de voz, o som solta-se donde &eacute; emitido e como leve coluna de fumo busca o ar transparente, onde vogam as andorinhas. Cada vez mais alto, o som atravessa as nuvens... </div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer9','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer8','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer10','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer9','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer10" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:275px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">	Quando chove e as gotas de chuva tilintam nas &aacute;guas dos rios e dos lagos, os sons que subiram regressam &agrave; Terra. Todos juntos, em grande confus&atilde;o, escorrem pelas correntes de &aacute;gua, em caudais de m&uacute;sica, em ondas, em cascatas, e v&atilde;o ter ao mar.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer10','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer9','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer11','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer10','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer11" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:275px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Os sons mais pesados v&atilde;o para o fundo. Os outros permanecem &agrave; superf&iacute;cie e, levados pelo balan&ccedil;o das ondas, navegam, de mistura com algas, penas de gaivotas, bocadinhos de luz e de prata, roubados ao Sol.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer11','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer10','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer12','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer11','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer12" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:275px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Estava eu na praia, a contemplar um p&ocirc;r de Sol (sou coleccionador de pores de Sol, n&atilde;o sei se sabem), quando uma musiquinha suave me trespassou os ouvidos.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer12','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer11','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer13','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer12','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer13" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:275px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%"> 
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Os &oacute;culos j&aacute; embaciados da poalha da maresia ficaram ainda mais embaciados, porque, de repente, me lembrei de que tinha ouvido aquela m&uacute;sica &agrave; beira de um coreto pela m&atilde;o do meu av&ocirc; Domingos. Portanto, h&aacute; muito e muito tempo...
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">N&atilde;o estava a inventar.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer13','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer12','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer14','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer13','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer14" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:275px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%"> Para ter a certeza, aflorei a m&uacute;sica aos l&aacute;bios, num sussurro de um assobio, que voou em direc&ccedil;&atilde;o &agrave;s nuvens rosadas do entardecer.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Foi ent&atilde;o que resolvi escrever esta hist&oacute;ria.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%"></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer14','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer13','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="35%"><a href="imprimir.pdf" target="_blank"> <img src="../../../images/impre.jpg" align="left" border="0" width="20" height="20"></a><a href="javascript:MM_openBrWindow('../../../pop_votar.aspx?Mes=10&Dia=01','','menubar=no,width=270,height=170')"><img src="../../../images/votar_over.gif" align="right" border="0" width="67" height="20"></a></td></tr></table></div> 
